	.string "seven tough TRAINERS in a row.\p"
	.string "{PLAYER} received some RIBBONS!$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_PutRibbonOnMons:
	.string "{PLAYER} put the RIBBONS on\n"
	.string "the challenger POKéMON.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_DescribeFeelingsAboutBattleTower:
	.string "Yo, you got a minute?\p"
	.string "Can you tell me your vibe when you're\n"
	.string "starting a BATTLE TOWER match, or\l"
	.string "when you've either won or lost?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_FeelWhatWhenYouBegin:
	.string "Safe, so how you feeling when you're\n"
	.string "about to start the match?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_FeelWhatWhenYouveWon:
	.string "What's the vibe when you've secured\n"
	.string "the win?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_FeelWhatWhenYouveLost:
	.string "And what's going through your head\n"
	.string "when you take a loss?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_DontThinkMuchAboutit:
	.string "Oh, so you're just moving cold?\n"
	.string "No stress, I see you.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ChangedYourMind:
	.string "Huh? You changed your mind?\n"
	.string "Bit of a flip-flopper, aren't you?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ThatsHowYouFeel:
	.string "Okay, so that's the energy?\n"
	.string "That's proper original, trust.\p"
	.string "Love for that!$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_WinsInRowRecorded:
	.string "The amount of matches you win in a row\n"
	.string "gets recorded.\p"
	.string "I better not go out sad in some\n"
	.string "embarrassing way!$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_CanLeaveUntilLossOrSevenWins:
	.string "Once you've stepped into the TOWER,\n"
	.string "you can't leave until you lose or\l"
	.string "smoke seven TRAINERS in a row.\p"
	.string "You better be certain you're actually\n"
	.string "ready for the smoke.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_LookForwardToAnotherChallenge:
	.string "We're looking forward to your next run!$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_WhichLevelMode:
	.string "The BATTLE ROOM has two tiers:\n"
	.string "Level 50 and Open Level.\l"
	.string "Which one you rolling with?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_OkayToSaveBeforeEntering:
	.string "Before stepping into the BATTLE ROOM,\n"
	.string "we gotta save. You cool with that?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ShowYouToBattleRoom:
	.string "I'll show you to the\n"
	.string "{STR_VAR_1} BATTLE ROOM now.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_RecordLastMatch:
	.string "Wanna record that last TOWER match\n"
	.string "on your FRONTIER PASS?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_NotEnoughValidMonsEnd:
	.string "Come back and see me when you're ready.$"

