BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_WelcomSingleBattle:
	.string "Where the levels of TRAINERS\n"
	.string "are proper put to the test!\p"
	.string "Welcome to the BATTLE TOWER!\p"
	.string "I'm your guide for the SINGLE\n"
	.string "BATTLE ROOMS.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_TakeSinglesChallenge:
	.string "You wanna take on the SINGLE\n"
	.string "BATTLE ROOM challenge?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ExplainSinglesChallenge:
	.string "The TOWER's SINGLE BATTLE ROOMS\n"
	.string "are for 1v1 battles with three POKéMON.\p"
	.string "We got bare rooms for team battles.\p"
	.string "In each one, seven TRAINERS\n"
	.string "are waiting for the smoke.\p"
	.string "If you manage to smoke all seven,\n"
	.string "you'll bag some Battle Points.\p"
	.string "If you gotta stop, just save the game.\p"
	.string "If you don't save before hopping off,\n"
	.string "you're disqualified, simple.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_SelectThreeMons:
	.string "Now pick the three POKéMON\n"
	.string "you're entering with.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_WelcomeDoubleBattle:
	.string "Where the levels of TRAINERS\n"
	.string "are proper put to the test!\p"
	.string "Welcome to the BATTLE TOWER!\p"
	.string "I'm your guide for the DOUBLE\n"
	.string "BATTLE ROOMS.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_TakeDoublesChallenge:
	.string "You wanna take on the DOUBLE\n"
	.string "BATTLE ROOM challenge?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ExplainDoublesChallenge:
	.string "The TOWER's DOUBLE BATTLE ROOMS\n"
	.string "are for 2v2 battles with four POKéMON.\p"
	.string "In each of these rooms, seven\n"
	.string "TRAINERS are waiting for you.\p"
	.string "If you manage to smoke all seven,\n"
	.string "you'll bag some Battle Points.\p"
	.string "If you gotta stop, just save the game.\p"
	.string "If you don't save before hopping off,\n"
	.string "you're disqualified, simple.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_PleaseSelectFourMons:
	.string "Now pick the four POKéMON\n"
	.string "you're entering with.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_WelcomeMultiBattle:
	.string "Where the levels of TRAINERS\n"
	.string "are proper put to the test!\p"
	.string "Welcome to the BATTLE TOWER!\p"
	.string "I'm your guide for the MULTI\n"
	.string "BATTLE ROOMS.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_TakeMultisChallenge:
	.string "You wanna take on the MULTI\n"
	.string "BATTLE ROOM challenge?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ExplainMultisChallenge:
	.string "The TOWER's MULTI BATTLE ROOMS\n"
	.string "are for tag-team battles.\p"
	.string "You gotta partner up with a TRAINER\n"
	.string "here and enter with two POKéMON each.\p"
	.string "We got a room called the BATTLE SALON\n"
	.string "where you can meet other TRAINERS.\p"
	.string "Find a partner there to roll with.\p"
	.string "Once you're linked up, I'll show you\n"
	.string "to a MULTI BATTLE ROOM.\p"
	.string "Seven tag teams are waiting for you.\p"
	.string "If you manage to smoke all seven,\n"
	.string "you'll bag some Battle Points.\p"
	.string "If you gotta stop, just save the game.\p"
	.string "If you don't save before hopping off,\n"
	.string "you're disqualified, simple.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_PleaseSelectTwoMons:
	.string "Now pick the two POKéMON\n"
	.string "you're entering with.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_WelcomeLinkMultiBattle:
	.string "Where the levels of TRAINERS\n"
	.string "are proper put to the test!\p"
	.string "Welcome to the BATTLE TOWER!\p"
	.string "I'm your guide for the LINK MULTI\n"
	.string "BATTLE ROOMS.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_TakeLinkMultisChallenge:
	.string "You wanna take on the LINK MULTI\n"
	.string "BATTLE ROOM challenge?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ExplainLinkMultisChallenge:
	.string "The TOWER's MULTI BATTLE ROOMS\n"
	.string "are for tag-teaming with a friend.\p"
	.string "Link up using Wireless Adapters\n"
	.string " or a Game Link cable.\p"
	.string "Partner with your friend and enter\n"
	.string "two different kinds of POKéMON.\p"
	.string "In the room, seven tag teams\n"
	.string "are waiting for the challenge.\p"
	.string "If you manage to smoke all seven,\n"
	.string "you'll bag some Battle Points.\p"
	.string "Just know you can't interrupt this\n"
	.string "challenge once you start.\p"
	.string "You gotta go through all seven\n"
	.string "matches in one go. No breaks!$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_PleaseSelectTwoMons2:
	.string "Now pick the two POKéMON\n"
	.string "you're entering with.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_LinkMultiOnlyForTwoPlayers:
	.string "The LINK MULTI BATTLE ROOM is only\n"
	.string "for two linked players, fam.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_FriendAlsoSelectedMon:
	.string "Your friend also picked\n"
	.string "the POKéMON {STR_VAR_1}.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_FriendAlsoSelectedMons:
	.string "Your friend also picked the\n"
	.string "POKéMON {STR_VAR_1} and {STR_VAR_2}.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_FriendChoseDifferentLvlMode:
	.string "Your friend picked a different\n"
	.string "battle level.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ChooseDifferentMonsMatchLvlMode:
	.string "Pick two POKéMON different from your\n"
	.string "friend's, match the level you want,\l"
	.string "and register again.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_SaveGameBeforeShowingIn:
	.string "Saving the game before showing\n"
	.string "you in. Hold tight.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_CongratsDefeatedMaiden:
	.string "Big moves!\n"
	.string "You smoked the SALON MAIDEN\l"
	.string "and swept all seven TRAINERS!$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_AwardYouTheseBattlePoints:
	.string "Seeing as your levels are unreal,\n"
	.string "here's your Battle Point(s).$"

BattleFrontier_Text_ObtainedXBattlePoints:
	.string "{PLAYER} bagged {STR_VAR_1} Battle Point(s).$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_RulesAreListed:
	.string "BATTLE TOWER rules are listed here.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ReadWhichHeading:
	.string "Which part you wanna read?$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ExplainTowerRules:
	.string "The BATTLE TOWER has four modes:\n"
	.string "SINGLE, DOUBLE, MULTI, and LINK MULTI.\p"
	.string "Each mode has its own rooms.\p"
	.string "Speak to the guide for the specific\n"
	.string "vibe you're looking for.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ExplainMonRules:
	.string "Depending on the room, you need\n"
	.string "a certain amount of POKéMON.\p"
	.string "SINGLE BATTLE needs three.\p"
	.string "DOUBLE BATTLE needs four, and\n"
	.string "the MULTI modes both need two.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ExplainSalonRules:
	.string "The BATTLE SALON is where you find\n"
	.string " a partner for the MULTI BATTLE ROOM.\p"
	.string "Pick the best partner by checking\n"
	.string "their POKéMON and what they're moving.\p"
	.string "You can pick a new partner after\n"
	.string "sweeping seven matches in a row.$"

BattleFrontier_BattleTowerLobby_Text_ExplainMultiLinkRules:
	.string "LINK MULTI is for you and a friend\n"
	.string "to take on a challenge together.\p"
	.string "You gotta be linked via Wireless\n"
	.string "Adapters or a Game Link cable.\p"
	.string "Pick two POKéMON at the counter.\p"
	.string "They gotta be different from what\n"
	.string "your friend is using.\p"
	.string "And remember, no breaks once you\n"
	.string "start. You gotta run the whole set.$"

